		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
		
		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Bard Lambent Armor</FONT><BR>
Zone : Temple of Solusek Ro<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ariel"><B>Updated:</B> December 7th 1999</FONT><BR><BR>

Walthin Fireweaver and Cyrissa make Lambent armor.  This is bard only armor. <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=94">Lambent Breastplate:</A> (Cyrissa)  Basalt Carapace (from basalt gargoyles in lower guk),
Gypsy Lute (from Mistmoore), Lambent Ruby; <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=95">Lambent Helm:</A>  (Cyrissa)  Opaline Helm (from Deepwater Goblins), Mudwater Rune
(From Lizard Fanatic), Lambent Star Ruby; <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=96">Lambent Vambraces:</A>  (Cyrissa)  Fiery Vambraces (from Solusek Champion), The Top
Portion of the Rune of the One Eye (Spawns on Choon), Lambent Sapphire; <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=97">Lambent Bracers:</A>  (Cyrissa)  Dark Boned Bracelet (From Greater Dark Boned
Skeletons), Griffenne Charm (From Griffenne's), Lambent Fire Opal; <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=98">Lambent Gauntlets:</A> (Walthin)  <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=333">Shin Gauntlets</A> (From Shin Knight in Guk), <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=320">Black Silk
Gloves</A> (from Deathly Usher in Mistmoore), Lambent Star Ruby; <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=83">Lambent Greaves:</A>  (Walthin)  Icy Greaves: (Elite Goblin Guards in Permafrost), Shin
Greaves (Shin Ghoul Knghts in Lower Guk), Lambent Fire Opal; <BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/armor_detail.php3?search=131">Lambent Boots:</A>  (Walthin)  Firewalker Boots (From Solusek Mage), Middle Portion of
the Rune of the One Eye (Froon), Lambent Sapphire. <BR><BR>

<B>Lambent Gems:</B><BR>  
In order to get lambent armor, you must first get Lambent gems.  These are made as follows:<BR><BR>
<B>Lambent Fire Opal:</B> 2 fire opals (purchasable from Ginni) and 1 Lambent stone (found on Hill Giants, Sand Giants, or Griffins), Give to Orstorm; <BR>
<B>Lambent Star Ruby:</B> 2 Star Rubies and 1 Lambent Stone, Give to Ginni;<BR>
<B>Lambent Sapphire:</B>  2 Sapphires and 1 Lambent Stone,   Give to Gardern;<BR>
<B>Lambent Ruby:</B>  2 Rubies and 1 Lambent Stone, Give to Vilissia.<BR><BR>

<B>NEW:</B> Click <A HREF="http://www.loreseekers.com/files/lambent_armor.zip">HERE</A> to download a single page checklist for this quest that is in Word '97 format. A handy tool to help organize all the steps involved.<BR><BR>
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
